sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant DB

User->>Frontend: Browse locations
Frontend->>API: GET /api/locations
API->>DB: Query locations
alt DB error
DB-->>API: error
API-->>Frontend: 500 with error message
Frontend-->>User: Show error state
else Success
DB-->>API: rows
API-->>Frontend: 200 location list
Frontend-->>User: Render locations
end
